{
  "text": "The presence of genes encoding TEM, SHV, OXA, CTX-M, and CMY type \u2424-lactamases was studied by specific PCRs [CITATION_1] . All obtained amplicons were sequenced on both strands, and sequences were compared with those included in the GenBank database and at the Lahey Clinic website (http://www.lahey.org /Studies/) to identify the \u2424-lactamase genes.",
  "citation_candidates": [
    "972552",
